Private Sub Detail_Format(Cancel As Integer, FormatCount As Integer)
    On Error GoTo SubError
    Dim criteria As String
    Dim exhjudrs As Recordset
    Dim Exnum As Long
    Dim rpt As Report
    Dim strMessage As String
    Dim jcount As Integer
    Dim intHorSize As Integer, intVerSize As Integer
    Exnum = Me.tbEXN
    Set rpt = Me
    strMessage = Exnum
    With rpt
        'Set scale to pixels, and set FontName and
        'FontSize properties.
        .ScaleMode = 3
        .FontName = "Arial" ' to save toner could find a ligher, hollow font?
' CHANGE FONTSIZE NUMBER TO MAKE EXN BIGGER OR SMALLER ------------------------
        .FontSize = 180 '180 seems to work for most printers
        '.FontWeight = 100 no work, Darn, would like to save toner.
    End With
    ' Horizontal width.
    intHorSize = rpt.TextWidth(strMessage)
    ' Vertical height.
    intVerSize = rpt.TextHeight(strMessage)
    ' Calculate location of text to be displayed.
' CHANGE CURRENTX to move EXN TO THE RIGHT OR LEFT BIGGER NUM MOVES TO LEFT ---
    rpt.CurrentX = 100  ' 100 seems to work with most printers
' CHANGE CURRENTY to move EXN UP OR DOWN BIGGER NUM MOVES DOWN ------------- ---
    rpt.CurrentY = 520 '  LazerJet IIP use 250, LazerJet 4050 use 520 ??
    ' Print text on Report object.
    rpt.Print strMessage
    ' rev 540
    If Me!TeamEx Then  ' Check box is not visible
      
      lblTeam.Caption = "TEAM PROJECT"
    Else
     
      lblTeam.Caption = ""
    End If
    criteria = "SELECT JUN, EXN FROM ExhibitJudges WHERE " & _
             "EXN = " & Exnum & " ORDER BY JUN"
    Set exhjudrs = CurrentDb().OpenRecordset(criteria, dbOpenDynaset)
    Me.tbJUN = ""
    jcount = 0
    With exhjudrs
    If .EOF Then Exit Sub
    Do While Not .EOF
        If jcount = 0 Then
          Me.tbJUN = Me.tbJUN & "Judge # " & !JUN & " ___"
        Else
          Me.tbJUN = Me.tbJUN & vbCrLf & "Judge # " & !JUN & " ___"
        End If
        jcount = jcount + 1
      .MoveNext
    Loop
   End With
   Exit Sub
SubError:
   MsgBox Err.Description
End Sub
